after deflecting widely from their entry trajectory, especially in relaxed\nclusters. They do not have a preferential location with respect to filaments\nand cannot collapse to form filaments. The remaining pristine galaxies (30 -\n60%) are environmentally effected by cosmic filaments alone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2021 19:08:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-08"}
