ometric one given recently (in December 2020) by Gaia DR3\nas $22.3689\\pm 0.4056$ mas.\n  The positions of the components of the two systems on the evolutionary tracks\nand isochrones are plotted, which suggest that all components are solar-type\nmain sequence stars. Their most probable formation and evolution scenarios are\nalso discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Nov 2021 06:47:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-24"}
