isual images. Finally an analysis\nof the influence of the different YOLOv3's output scales on the detection is\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Nov 2021 08:04:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 17:32:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
