n. Finally, we explore\nthe preferential concentration and alignment of fibres within the flow,\nhighlighting the peculiar role of inertia and elasticity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Nov 2021 08:33:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 May 2022 13:17:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-24"}
