ate. Both the experimental method and the data-treatment procedure\npresented herein offer promising routes in the study of fundamental aspects of\nnucleation kinetics, particularly confinement effects, and are adaptable to\nother salts, pharmaceuticals, or biological crystals of interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Nov 2021 10:41:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 14:37:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 10:34:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
