 scenarios for the years 2030 and 2050,\nconsidering different assumptions about the cost of the surplus utilization of\nRES. The results show that LCSNG may vary from 47 to 319 EURO/MWh, according to\nthe different configurations, i.e., only in the best case scenario is the SNG\ncost comparable with the cost of natural gas, and hence does the P2G technology\nresult to be profitable\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Nov 2021 11:06:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-24"}
